@droidicus Cloud ML is not yet on 1.6 [ source ](https://cloud.google.com/ml-engine/docs/runtime-version-list) but I guess it will come at some point or you can manually force the installation.
@bhack As much as I agree with you I really think that just a gist would be enough for most people than a full tutorial especially since this is the first result when you google `distributed model_to_estimator`.
